## Notes

- **Config Path**: Update `_bmad/bmm/config.yaml` to `_personal-automation/{module}/config.yaml`
- **TTS Integration**: The bmad-speak.sh hook works with AgentVibes for voice output
- **Party Mode**: Keep reference to core party-mode workflow for multi-agent collaboration
- **Menu Items**: Add 3-5 focused workflows per agent (don't overcomplicate)
- **Persona**: Make it distinctive and memorable - each agent should feel different
